Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:07.85,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,いやぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:07.85,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:10.81,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,おっとさん おっかさん 助けて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:10.81,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,父親 母親 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.07,0:01:48.51,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,父上 見ていてください
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.07,0:01:48.51,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,父親 看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:55.12,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,この月島仁兵衛必ずや 江戸でのお勤めを　立派に果たしてまいります
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:55.12,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我月島仁兵衛一定會在江戶幹出一番事業來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:19.08,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと 江戸には 蟲奉行所には
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:19.08,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,在江戶　在蟲奉行所中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:22.67,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,父上のように 強いお人がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:22.67,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會有像父親那樣厲害的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:36.11,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,無涯樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:36.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,無涯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:45.06,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,今日も また 巣食っていやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:45.06,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也依然令人生厭地盤踞著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:57.19,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,江戸には いったいどんな猛者がいるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:57.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,在江戶會遇見怎樣的高手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:02:59.96,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,楽しみだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:02:59.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.78,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,第一話　月島仁兵衛　いざ参る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,月島仁兵衛參上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:14.45,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,おお なんと ここが江戸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:14.45,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,哇天啊　這就是江戶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:21.90,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,おはようございます
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:21.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:24.02,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,なんだあれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:24.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊那是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:32.25,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,拝啓 津軽の父上様
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:32.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,敬啟 遠在津輕的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:36.60,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,自分は本日より蟲奉行所なるところでお勤めを始めます
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:36.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,從今日開始我將就職於名為蟲奉行所的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:40.92,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,その蟲奉行所がいかなるところなのかはいまだにわかりません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:40.92,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,這個蟲奉行所到底是什麼地方 我尚且不知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:45.02,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,ですが 武士たる自分が決めた道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:45.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這是身為武士的我自己選擇的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.60,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,どのようなところであっても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,無論我身在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:50.93,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,粉骨砕身で お勤めにあたる覚悟で 蟲奉行所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:50.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我都做好了哪怕粉身碎骨也要盡忠職守的覺悟 前往蟲奉行所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:53.49,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,向かっておりません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:53.49,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我找不到在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:04:00.77,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,父上 江戸の人たちは迷子に冷たいでございます
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:04:00.77,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,父親 江戶的人們對迷途之人好冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:02.11,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,あの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:02.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:03.30,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:03.30,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.62,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,どこか お怪我でも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.62,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,您是不是哪兒受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.56,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,かたじけない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:15.45,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,しみ入ります　この甘み この優しさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:15.45,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,真是沁人心脾 這份甜美 這份體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.90,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,申し遅れました
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起還沒來得及自報家門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:24.84,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,自分は蟲奉行所のお勤めに参った月島仁兵衛と申します
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:24.84,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,在下是前往蟲奉行所報道之人 名叫月島仁兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:26.57,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,まぁ 蟲奉行所で
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:26.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是要去蟲奉行所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:27.42,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:27.42,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:30.45,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,私は春と申します
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:30.45,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫做小春
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:32.59,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,この茶屋の娘です
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:32.59,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,是這家茶屋的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.37,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,なんと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.37,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:36.72,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,どうされました
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:36.72,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:38.54,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,いえ なんでも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:38.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.08,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,お春殿 ご家族で ここを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.08,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,小春小姐 這裏是您一家人在經營嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:45.60,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,ええ おじいさんと二人で
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:45.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我和爺爺兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:48.49,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,二人 ご両親は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:48.49,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人…那您父母呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:52.86,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,私が幼い頃に亡くなりました
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:52.86,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,在我還小的時候就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:55.19,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ そっ それは失礼を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:55.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這真是失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:58.56,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,いえ 江戸では よくある話ですから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:58.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裏 這在江戶是常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.90,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,よくある話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,常有的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.44,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,お春 焼けたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.44,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,小春 燒好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.32,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,は～い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.32,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.96,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,道案内まで かたじけない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,還幫我引路 真是感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:16.29,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,いいんです 仁兵衛様はどうして蟲奉行所に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:16.29,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不必客氣 仁兵衛大人為什麼要去蟲奉行所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:22.59,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,本当は 津軽にいる父が呼ばれたのです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:22.59,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,其實受命的本是在津輕的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.80,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,しかし 父は動けぬ身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.80,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是父親身體行動不便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:37.22,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,ですから 自分が代わりにお上のお勤めを果たしたいと 父に申し出たのです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:37.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我向父親提議 由我去代替他為朝廷辦事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:43.00,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,ご立派ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:43.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,您真了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:43.84,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,いえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:43.84,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:48.54,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ お春殿こそやはり ご立派
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:48.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,小春小姐才是 實在是太不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:50.58,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,私 嬉しいんです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:50.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:54.25,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,知ってます 仁兵衛様
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:54.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,仁兵衛大人 您知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:57.14,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,蟲奉行所がどのようにしてできたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:57.14,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,蟲奉行所是如何設立的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:04.91,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,今から１０年前 享保６年に庶民の要求や不満を聞くために
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:04.91,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前 也就是享保六年的時候 為傾聽庶民的訴求與不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:06.93,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,目安箱が作られました
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:06.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,請願箱應運而生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:11.74,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,江戸のみんなが投書したことで作られたのが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:11.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,應江戶民眾的投書請願而設的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.16,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,蟲奉行所です
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.16,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,正是蟲奉行所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:17.90,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,私もたくさん投書したんです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:17.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我也投了不少信函
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:25.03,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,私の両親みたいに襲われないよう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:25.03,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我祈求政府能保護好大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:28.04,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,みんなを蟲から守ってくださいって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:28.04,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,以免像我父母那樣遭受蟲子的襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:32.78,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,お春殿 あの　その蟲とは いったい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:32.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,小春小姐 請問 你說的蟲到底是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:37.59,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ お春殿はここに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:37.59,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,小春小姐請待在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.06,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,どうなされた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.06,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:53.10,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,なっ人の　皮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:53.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,什…　人…皮?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:05.38,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,にっ 似ている　あのときの化け物に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:05.38,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好像　那時候的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:15.78,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:15.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.50,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,待つんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:51.11,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,蟲奉行所の者がこちらへ向かっている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:51.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,蟲奉行所的人正趕往這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.50,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,私たちに任せるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:58.05,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,蟲奉行所のお方でしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:58.05,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,您是蟲奉行所的人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.94,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,松ノ原小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.94,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫松之原小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:04.66,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,蟲奉行所を監督している キミは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:04.66,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,任蟲奉行所監督一職　你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:07.66,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,月島仁兵衛と申します
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:07.66,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,在下名叫月島仁兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:11.27,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,父の代わりに お勤めすべく江戸に参りました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:11.27,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,是代替家父 前來江戶任職的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:14.02,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,源十郎殿のご子息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:14.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你是源十郎先生家的公子?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:19.32,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,私が呼んだのは津軽藩の剣術指南役である父上だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:19.32,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我邀請的可是你那身在津輕藩擔任劍術教頭的父親哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:24.12,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,父は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:24.12,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,父親他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:27.35,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,もう 動けないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:27.35,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不能再走動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:31.33,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,父の左足を 自分が奪ったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:31.33,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,是在下 奪走了父親的左腿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:39.95,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,かつて 自分が藩主様のご子息のお供をしていたときのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:39.95,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,那是過去在下侍奉著藩主大人之子時候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:42.39,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,自分は出会ったのです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:42.39,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,在下遇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:44.44,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,熊が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:44.44,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,熊都被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.93,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,今のような化け物に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,像剛剛那樣的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:50.43,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,しかし 自分は武士の息子でありながら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:50.43,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 在下身為武士之子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:58.81,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,藩主様のご子息に恥をかかせてしまいました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:58.81,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,卻讓藩主大人的公子蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.95,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（致し方ない）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.95,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我也是逼不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:02.20,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,すべては 自分の責任　しかし その責めを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:02.20,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是在下的責任 然而父親他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:03.57,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,申し訳ございません
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:03.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,臣罪該萬死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:05.64,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,父は 自分の代わりに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:05.64,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,卻代替我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:08.25,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,父上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:08.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.23,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,父上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:20.98,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,自分が ふがいないばかりに父は 左足も地位も出世も
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:20.98,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為在下的窩囊無用 父親失去了左腿 地位 仕途
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:22.73,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,すべて失ったのです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:22.73,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:28.53,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,ですから 自分は せめて父が誇れる強い武士になり
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:28.53,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,因此在下至少要成為能讓父親引以為傲的強大武士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:32.36,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,父の代わりにお勤めを果たしたいのです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:32.36,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,替父親履行其職責
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:33.73,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,どうか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:33.73,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,望准許
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:40.24,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,悪いけど 今のように 蟲を相手にするのが蟲奉行所の勤め
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:40.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 蟲奉行所的職責就是剷除像剛剛那樣的蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:43.26,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,並の者には務まらないんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:43.26,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,尋常人可幹不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:45.58,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:45.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:50.20,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,決して 並でないところご覧に入れてみせます
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:50.20,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,在下一定會讓您看到我不尋常之處
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:52.85,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,いや そういう意味じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:52.85,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不是這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:54.24,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,てえへんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:54.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:55.78,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,どうなされた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:55.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:58.24,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,女を さらっていきやがったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:58.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,有女人被擄走了
