Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:00.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,是糰子屋的小春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:03.30,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,お春殿が  蟲は どこへ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:03.30,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,你說小春小姐? 蟲子往哪邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:04.21,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,あっちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:04.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:07.84,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,お春殿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:07.84,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,小春小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:11.36,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,私の両親みたいに襲われないよう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:11.36,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我祈求政府能保護好大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:14.38,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,みんなを 蟲から守ってくださいって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:14.38,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,以免像我父母那樣遭受蟲子的襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.49,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,いや いやあ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.49,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要
