Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.66,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,是屋牢蜘蛛干的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:41.35,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,やっ やだな 蜘蛛なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:41.35,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,真 真討厭啊 蜘蛛什麼的
