Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:15.59,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,いやああ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:15.59,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:27.53,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,助けに来るのが遅くなって 申し訳ございません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:27.53,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,十分抱歉沒能及時前來相救
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:35.32,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,仁兵衛樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:35.32,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,仁兵衛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:43.32,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,いくぞ これが江戸での初陣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:43.32,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了 這就是我在江戶的首戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.77,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,月島仁兵衛 参る
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.77,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,月島仁兵衛 參上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.70,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,焦るな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,不可焦躁
